<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَلَمَّا كَانَتْ الْقِسْمَةُ مِنْ تَعَلُّقَاتِ الشَّرِكَةِ كَالشُّفْعَةِ نَاسَبَ أَنْ يَذْكُرَهَا عَقِبَهَا فَقَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ــ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[حاشية الصاوي]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5"> قَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c4">[نَاسَبَ أَنْ يَذْكُرَهَا]</span> : أَيْ الْقِسْمَةَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c4">[عَقِبَهَا]</span> : أَيْ الشُّفْعَةِ. وَمَعْنَى هَذَا الدُّخُولِ أَنَّهُ لَمَّا كَانَ كُلٌّ مِنْ الْقِسْمَةِ وَالشُّفْعَةِ تَابِعًا لِلشَّرِكَةِ ذَكَرَهُمَا مُتَوَالِيَيْنِ بَعْدَهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>